This map was made in 6 or 7, could have been 8 hours.

Any ways I hope you enjoy, I rendered it with as high quality as my PC let me.
Any sort of creative criticism is more then welcome.

If you do download the map and put it on your server do send me the IP, either post it in here, send it to me in here, or send it to me on steam (stead name: Jouls_css)
